<D>__{...in the chocolate, please, mom...}
<C>__{michael}
<P>__{(repeating after her)}
<D>__{...please, mom.}
<A>__{she pours the cereal in his hot chocolate.}
<C>__{daisy}
<D>__{yuck, that's gross, how can you eat that?}
<C>__{amy}
<D>__{come on, come on, let's get going, or you're going to be late for school.}
<A>__{michael begins to eat his breakfast, his gaze still fixed on the weatherman's forecast on tv. as amy fills the cat's bowl with pellets, tiger rushes over to join the rest of the family.}
