<P>__{(to his sister)}
<D>__{you promised not to tell.}
<C>__{amy}
<D>__{does he go to your school?}
<A>__{michael doesn't answer. daisy shakes her head.}
<C>__{amy }
<P>__{(pretending to be indifferent)}
<D>__{very well. if you don't want to tell me about it...}
